source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SEQ_00<tab>The face of an injured Sekiseigumi blade is twisted in pain.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SEQ_00<tab>Ce samouraï du Sekiseigumi a le visage défiguré par la douleur.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_TODO_01<tab>Use the milky white salve on the injured Sekiseigumi blade.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_TODO_01<tab>Traiter le samouraï du Sekiseigumi blessé
avec la pommade analgésique

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_000<tab>Ugh... <pant> I must...get word to my brother. But these wounds... I cannot.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_000<tab>Urrgh... Je... Je dois l'avertir... ngh... tout de suite... M-mais je...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_001<tab>You... You don't look to be one of them. I take great risk trusting you, but I've no other choice. Nor the time. Please, hear me out.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_001<tab>Ah... Je croyais qu'il était revenu... urgh... pour finir le travail... J-je sais pas si je peux te faire confiance... mais j'ai plus le choix... S'il te plaît... Aide-moi... Nrgh...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_002<tab>I am a blade of the Sekiseigumi, and I <wince> came under attack by a foreign devil while on patrol. I fear my fellow blade may meet with the same fate if not warned.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_002<tab>J... ugh... J'étais en train de patrouiller... quand je me suis fait attaquer par un malfrat... Mon camarade... grhg... pourrait être le prochain...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_003<tab>I... I will survive. <grunt> But my Sekiseigumi brother must be told of this attack. He patrols an alley off Kogane Dori. Please, go with haste.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_003<tab>T-tu dois le prévenir... Ngh... Il monte la garde dans le chemin de traverse de Kogane-dori... Fais vite, je t'en prie...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_004<tab>I... I will survive. <grunt> But my Sekiseigumi brother must be told of this attack. He patrols an alley off Kogane Dori. Please, go with haste.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_004<tab>T'inquiète pas pour moi... argh... j-je survivrai... Va voir mon camarade, et... ngh... dis-lui que je me suis fait attaquer... Fais vite, je t'en prie...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIB02814_000_011<tab>My brother blade? Attacked by a foreign devil? And one so skilled as to injure one of the Sekiseigumi's most gifted... Rushing after this fiend on my own would be rushing to my own death.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIB02814_000_011<tab>... Mon frère d'armes a été attaqué<var 1D /var>!? M-mais c'est pourtant l'un des meilleurs épéistes du Sekiseigumi<var 1D /var>! Son agresseur doit être in<var 16 /var>croya<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment puissant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIB02814_000_012<tab>I would ask your help in this. Use this milky white salve on the injured Sekiseigumi blade that sent you to me. For my part, I will send for reinforcements from the barracks.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIB02814_000_012<tab>Tenez<var 1D /var>! Traitez ses blessures avec ça. Je vais aller demander des renforts à la caserne<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_020<tab>Did you see word to my brother blade?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_020<tab>Urrgh... Ah, c'est toi... T-tu as trouvé mon camarade<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_021<tab>He sent you back with this salve? <groan> Thank you. And thank the gods he is safe.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_021<tab>... Ouuh, merci... Il t'a donné cette pommade avant d'aller chercher des renforts... C'est une excellente décision...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_022<tab>Worry not. My pain is mostly gone. My apologies for pulling you into this. But I see now I was right to trust you.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_022<tab>T'en fais pas, la douleur est déjà beaucoup moins intense... Je suis désolé de t'avoir mêlé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à tout ça...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_023<tab>As I told you, my attackers hail from across the seas. Violence is forbidden in Kugane, but those from abroad have little love for our laws.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_023<tab>Il est défendu de se battre à Kugane, mais le malfrat qui m'a attaqué se moque de nos lois...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_024<tab>My brother blade and I broke up their illicit dealings some time ago. No doubt they did not take kindly to that. My guess is they gathered their gil and hired an assassin.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_024<tab>Il y a quelque temps de ça, mon camarade et moi avons surpris des individus du continent en train de faire des transactions illégales. Visiblement, ils ont pas apprécié qu'on se mêle de leurs affaires, et ils ont envoyé un assassin pour nous éliminer.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_025<tab>Little did they know, we Sekiseigumi are not so easily killed. I hazard my brethren blades have already hunted these scoundrels down and gaoled them by now.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_025<tab>À l'heure qu'il est, ce gros balourd doit déjà être sous les verrous. Le Sekiseigumi a quelques poids lourds dans ses rangs.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_026<tab>You did us a service this day. As one who wears the haori of the Sekiseigumi, on behalf of us all, I thank you.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ711_02814_SAMURAIA02814_000_026<tab>En tout cas, je te remercie pour ton aide. Le Sekiseigumi te doit une fière chandelle.
